name: La dualità piece #37
description:
"Part of a limited 333 piece collection.

   La dualità takes the most historically relevant pieces of art, and reimagines them using world renowned styles of art.


   Everything from the style of brush strokes to the coloring is used to reimagine each piece. Famous art styles used in this collection includes Da Vinci, Raphael, Van Gogh, and many others"
